    },
    "可以为推送设置不同的铃声" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Different ringtones can be set for push notifications"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "可对通知设置中断级别" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Notification interruption level can be set"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "可选参数值：\nlevel=active: 默认值，系统会立即亮屏显示通知。\n*  支持数字 level=-1 小于0 都代表 active\nlevel=timeSensitive:  时效性通知,专注模式下可显示通知。\n*  支持数字 level=0\nlevel=passive：仅添加到列表，不会亮屏提醒\n*  支持数字 level=1\nlevel=critical: 暂时不可用,等待苹果授权中..\n*\t重要提醒，静音或专注模式可正常提醒\n*  支持数字(2-10) level=2 声音最小 level=10 声音最大 ," : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Optional Parameter Values:  \n\nlevel=active: Default value, the system will immediately wake the screen to display the notification.  \n* Supports numeric values: level=-1 or any value less than 0 represents active.  \n\nlevel=timeSensitive: Time-sensitive notification, can be displayed even in Focus mode.  \n* Supports numeric value: level=0.  \n\nlevel=passive: Adds to the list only, without waking the screen for notification.  \n* Supports numeric value: level=1.  \n\nlevel=critical: Temporarily unavailable, awaiting Apple authorization.  \n* Important alerts can bypass silent or Focus mode.  \n* Supports numeric values: level=2 for the lowest sound level, up to level=10 for the highest sound level."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "右上角点击耳机查看所有铃声" : {
      "localizations" : {
